1.title: Comenzó el terror

episode of.title: La Familia de al Lado (TV Series 2010–2011)

1.plot: A wedding is taking place in the Gardens of the Fabres mansion; they are celebrating the marriage of Ignacia and Gonzalo. Daniel is upset with Ignacia when he finds out Leonardo is living in this house and that he is Hugo's twin brother who was Ignacia's first husband. Ignacia takes Gonzalo to Leonardo's room to introduce the two men. Carola gives Ignacia the letter that Hugo left her before he died. Pilar and Gonzalo find Pedro dead; he was the gardener of the Fabres mansion.
